race.description: Quickmix Concrete Group (N/P) Stake Pr2 Division2
race.comment: BOURNE DRAMA (2) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 13 lengths sixth (18.66) last time in a Grade 6 at this track over 305m. Has the ability and looks a key chance. RALPH THE RAT (1) boasts a strong record this course with three wins and two minors from nine tries. Comes off a (18.11) win last time, scoring by one length in a TG1-4W over 305m at this track. Can feature in the finish. COMPTON BOWIE (7) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (18.05) last time in a TG1-4W at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Leading chance. BRAGGING RIGHTS (5) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.
